title: Ep 142 - Birthday Party Hangover
description: The boys battled through one hell of a post-birthday hangover. Nick turned 34 yesterday so most of the boys took him out to celebrate. Needless to say, they got thirsty. As usual, they ran through a wide gambit of topics. Everything from adult diapers to Pokémon cards. Enjoy.
